				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Tieflings will wait for the gnomes to rescue them if the gnome have tools and their back wall is broken down whilst the tieflings are still in their cells.\r\n\r\nTheir out of combat behaviour has them huddle close to their own wall, hoping for rescue.\r\n\r\nIf combat starts, they give in and start smacking the wall as well."
				}
